# PaylaterType

Representing the available paylater channels used for invoice-related transactions.


## Enum


    * `Kredivo` (value: `'KREDIVO'`)

    * `Akulaku` (value: `'AKULAKU'`)

    * `Uangme` (value: `'UANGME'`)

    * `Billease` (value: `'BILLEASE'`)

    * `Cashalo` (value: `'CASHALO'`)

    * `Atome` (value: `'ATOME'`)
